    cons: ["No Bluetooth", "Ambidextrous shape may not suit palm grip", "Only 5 buttons"],
    summary: "The G Pro X Superlight 2 is the most popular mouse in competitive FPS. At 60g with the HERO 2 sensor, it offers zero-compromise wireless performance. Logitech's Lightforce switches combine optical speed with mechanical feel. If you play Valorant, CS2, or Apex competitively, this is the default choice."
