    cons: ["Very flat shape won't suit everyone", "4000Hz dongle sold separately", "Expensive"],
    summary: "At 54g, the Viper V3 Pro is the lightest wireless gaming mouse you can buy without feeling like it'll break. The 4000Hz polling rate option (with the separate dongle) provides the smoothest cursor movement available. If raw speed and minimal weight are your priorities, nothing else comes close."
  },
