    cons: ["Honeycomb shell collects dust", "Side buttons can feel mushy", "74g is mid-weight"],
    summary: "The Aerox 5 packs 9 programmable buttons into a lightweight shell — ideal for MMOs and MOBAs where you need quick access to abilities. The 180-hour battery life is the longest on this list by a huge margin, and IP54 rating means spilled drinks won't kill it."
  },
  {
    name: "Logitech G502 X Plus",
    badge: "Best Feature-Rich",
    price: 160,
    sensor: "HERO 25K",
    dpi: 25600,
